title: Call of Duty 1 and call of duty united offensive-online noinstal
description:
Call Of Duty 1 And Call of duty United offensive with working online multiplayer for united offensive. Version 1.5/1.51


1. First run the Call Of Duty MPSettings .reg file to load the correct game settings to your computer.

2. To Play call of duty 1 singleplayer browse the Call of Duty folder and lunch CoDSP.

3. To Play call of duty united offensive singleplayer browse the Call of Duty folder and lunch CoDUOSP.

4. To play call of duty united offensive online multiplayer browse the Call of Duty folder and lunch CoDUOMP. Wen the game starts browse for servers in favorites to see the available servers
